                        </math>’s in the RREF of the non-augmented coefficient matrix of the system. This number of leading <math>
                           <latex>1</latex>
                        </math>’s can be less than the number of variables in the system.</para.body>
                  </para>
					             <para>
                     <para.body>Therefore the statement in question is false.</para.body>
